HEADWORD: fanwort
<hw>fanwort</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a common aquatic plant (<spn>Cabomba
caroliniana</spn>) of eastern North America having floating and
submerged leaves and white yellow-spotted flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> water-shield, <spn>Cabomba
caroliniana</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
